data.description: This brand-new home in The Links Estates, an Active 55+ Gated Community with beautiful club house, heated pool, spa, and community activities, is conveniently located in the heart of San Tan Valley. The home provides a spacious open floor plan with a large living space and kitchen, two large bedrooms and two bathrooms with ample storage and extra pantry space. The home comes fully equipped with new appliances, new vinyl flooring throughout the home, new roof, new AC unit and more. The covered patio and storage shed outside provide extra space for ideal indoor/outdoor living.
